  "title": "SITE SUPERVISOR/COORDINATOR",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist Site manager in overseeing the daily construction and site coordination works at various projects</li>\n  <li><u>On site supervise, coordinate and check quality of structural/architectural/M&amp;E works </u></li>\n  <li><u>Lead and monitor work of in-house workers or subcontractors</u></li>\n  <li><u>Monitor/ensure site safety requirements are enforced</u></li>\n</ul>\n<p><u>Requirements:</u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 2 ~ 3 years working experience</li>\n  <li>Familiar in construction materials will be an advantage</li>\n  <li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Able to commence work immediately</li>\n  <li>Singaporeans &amp; PR only</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Competitive remuneration package commensurate with qualifications will be offered.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>",
